OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784575122
OL,3,CCoroner warns more fatalities after
OL,4,Cdeath of woman, 87, who tripped on road
OL,6,FA coroner has recommended a system to
OL,7,Fprioritise urgent road repairs after
OL,8,Fan elderly woman tripped on a damaged
OL,9,Froad surface and later died.
OL,11,F87-year-old Beryl Barrett died after
OL,12,Fthe wheels on her walking frame got
OL,13,Fcaught in the road in Church Street in
OL,14,FWarsop near Mansfield days before
OL,15,FChristmas.
OL,17,FNottingham Coroner's Court heard that
OL,18,FMrs Barrett fractured her hip in the
OL,19,Ffall and died from bronchopneumonia at
OL,20,FKing's Mill Hospital in Sutton-in-
OL,21,FAshfield.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784575122
OL,3,CCoroner warns more fatalities after
OL,4,Cdeath of woman, 87, who tripped on road
OL,6,FAssistant coroner Nathanael Hartley
OL,7,Fconcluded on Monday that her death was
OL,8,Faccidental, but warned there may be a
OL,9,Frisk of more fatal incidents.
OL,11,FHe also found that the defect in the
OL,12,Froad that caused Mrs Barrett to trip
OL,13,Fwas not bad enough to require repair.
OL,15,FMrs Barrett was initially thought to
OL,16,Fhave tripped on a pothole which had
OL,17,Fnot been identified by inspectors 18
OL,18,Fdays before her fall, but the inquest
OL,19,Fheard there had been a
OL,20,Fmisunderstanding about which road
OL,21,Fdefect caused her fall.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784575122
OL,3,CCoroner warns more fatalities after
OL,4,Cdeath of woman, 87, who tripped on road
OL,6,FSteve Walton, a pre-construction
OL,7,Fdirector at Via East Midlands, which
OL,8,Fprovides road maintenance services for
OL,9,FNottinghamshire County Council, gave
OL,10,Fevidence to the inquest.
OL,12,FHe initially told the hearing that a
OL,13,Fpothole which had been thought to have
OL,14,Fcaused her fall had been missed during
OL,15,Fa road inspection on December 1st
OL,16,Fbecause the inspector deemed it not
OL,17,Fdeep enough to need filling in, but
OL,18,Fdid not consider the lower threshold
OL,19,Ffor potholes on pedestrian crossings.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784575122
OL,3,CCoroner warns more fatalities after
OL,4,Cdeath of woman, 87, who tripped on road
OL,6,FAfter reviewing dashcam images of the
OL,7,Ffall during his evidence, Mr Walton
OL,8,Fclarified that the pensioner had not
OL,9,Ftripped on that pothole, but on a less
OL,10,Fsevere road defect which did not
OL,11,Frequire repair.
OL,13,FMr Walton did not clarify what the
OL,14,Froad defect was.He told the inquest:
OL,15,F"At the time there was no actionable
OL,16,Fdefect recorded."
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@QO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784575122
OL,3,CCoroner warns more fatalities after
OL,4,Cdeath of woman, 87, who tripped on road
OL,6,FConcluding the inquest, Mr Hartley
OL,7,Fsaid: "The leading wheel of the three-
OL,8,Fwheeled frame became stuck in the
OL,9,Froad, which caused her to lose her
OL,10,Fbalance and fall.
OL,12,F"The defect thought to have been
OL,13,Fresponsible was not in fact the cause
OL,14,Fof the fall."
OL,16,FThe hole that was originally thought
OL,17,Fto have caused her to trip was filled
OL,18,Fon January 2, but has not been
OL,19,Fpermanently repaired.
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOUvD@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784575122
OL,3,CCoroner warns more fatalities after
OL,4,Cdeath of woman, 87, who tripped on road
OL,6,FThe coroner added: "The area where the
OL,7,Fwalker wheel became stuck was not an
OL,8,Factionable defect at that point.
OL,10,F"While I have concluded it was not
OL,11,Factionable, that does not mean it is
OL,12,Fnot serious and does not require the
OL,13,Fattention of Via East Midlands and
OL,14,FNottinghamshire County Council."
OL,16,FMr Walton told the inquest that
OL,17,Fpotholes that are 40mm deep on
OL,18,Fcarriageways or 20mm deep on
OL,19,Fpedestrian crossings need to be
OL,20,Frepaired.
OL,26,@nD@TOUrD@AOUvD@`O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784575122
OL,3,CCoroner warns more fatalities after
OL,4,Cdeath of woman, 87, who tripped on road
OL,6,FMr Hartley concluded that the fall
OL,7,F"more than minimally contributed to
OL,8,FBeryl's death because without it she
OL,9,Fwould not have died when she did".
OL,11,FThe coroner said he is concerned
OL,12,F"there's a future risk to others" and
OL,13,Fwill issue a prevention of future
OL,14,Fdeaths report to Nottinghamshire
OL,15,FCounty Council, Via East Midlands and
OL,16,Fthe UK Roads Liaison Group (UKRLG).
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@aO]tD@AOUtD@aO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784575122
OL,3,CCoroner warns more fatalities after
OL,4,Cdeath of woman, 87, who tripped on road
OL,6,FThe coroner said: "They do not appear
OL,7,Fto have a process in place that allows
OL,8,Fthem to triage referrals alerting them
OL,9,Fto concerns about the state of the
OL,10,Fhighways."
OL,12,FHe said no review of the road Mrs
OL,13,FBarrett fell on was done for 12 days
OL,14,Feven though it was suspected she had
OL,15,Ftripped on a pothole.
OL,17,FMr Hartley said there was no system to
OL,18,Fprioritise the most severe road
OL,19,Fdefects for urgent inspection.
OL,26,@nD@SOUrD@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784575122
OL,3,CCoroner warns more fatalities after
OL,4,Cdeath of woman, 87, who tripped on road
OL,6,FHe added that the UKRLG, which
OL,7,Fpublished a code of practice for
OL,8,Fmanaging roads, makes no specific
OL,9,Frecommendations about vulnerable
OL,10,Fpedestrians using walking aids with
OL,11,Fsmall wheels.
OL,13,FMrs Barrett's daughter Marie Rickman
OL,14,Ftold the coroner her mother "loved
OL,15,Flife" and was involved with her local
OL,16,Fcommunity and church.
OL,18,FShe said: "She went out every day `
OL,19,Fshe could not stand being in."She was
OL,20,Factive, she was fit, she kept herself
OL,21,Fgoing."
OL,26,@vD@]OUwD@EO]zD@KOU{D@^OU}D@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784575122
OL,3,CCoroner warns more fatalities after
OL,4,Cdeath of woman, 87, who tripped on road
OL,6,FThe Labour MP for Mansfield, Steve
OL,7,FYemm, had previously raised the need
OL,8,Ffor road repairs in the town with
OL,9,Fformer Prime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,10,Fin parliament.
OL,12,FHe asked the then Prime Minister
OL,13,Fwhether he agreed it was "time that
OL,14,Fthe council took action".
OL,16,FStarmer responded: "Can I send my
OL,17,Fdeepest sympathies to Beryl's family.
OL,18,FI will make sure the roads minister
OL,19,Fmeets the family at the earliest
OL,20,Fopportunity. It shows why tackling
OL,21,Fpotholes really matters."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784575122
OL,3,CCoroner warns more fatalities after
OL,4,Cdeath of woman, 87, who tripped on road
OL,6,FDavid Langford, Director of Highways,
OL,7,FTransport and Waste Management at
OL,8,FNottinghamshire County Council, said:
OL,10,F"We are deeply saddened to hear about
OL,11,Fthe passing of a resident in Warsop in
OL,12,FDecember, and our thoughts are with
OL,13,Ftheir family and friends.
OL,15,F"Any reports of incidents on our
OL,16,Fhighway resulting in injury are taken
OL,17,Fextremely seriously and are
OL,18,Finvestigated to establish the
OL,19,Fcircumstances in which they occurred.
OL,26,@rD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
