SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784575122
OL,3,CCoroner warns more fatalities after
OL,4,Cdeath of woman, 87, who tripped on road
OL,6,F"In this case, we do not feel that it
OL,7,Fis appropriate to comment further
OL,8,Funtil any relevant investigations have
OL,9,Ftaken place."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@MO]
